    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I've worked on trying to better explain this feature.\r\n\r\n[We are using](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/widgets/hierarchicalMenu.html#struct-HierarchicalMenuWidgetOptions-showParentLevel) the `showParentLevel` option from the helper. The thing that make this behaviour confusing is that it keeps the sibling values of the root. If that's considered a bug, we should consider filling it on the helper side and then integrate it in all InstantSearch libraries. I will close it for now, until we change the behavior in the Helper.",
